respect to 8 collective bargaining agreements covering most of our employees represented by the BCTGM. All of those
collective bargaining agreements expired in 2016.
In the fourth quarter of 2018, we executed a complete withdrawal from the Fund. We estimated a withdrawal liability of
$573 million, which represents our best estimate of the withdrawal liability absent an assessment from the Fund. We
anticipate receiving an assessment in 2019, and the ultimate withdrawal liability may change from the currently
