(or earlier for certain legacy Cadbury employees) are no longer eligible to participate in the defined benefit pension
plans. These employees are given an enhanced Company contribution to our employee defined contribution plans. For
those salaried and non-union hourly employees who are currently participating in the defined benefit pension plans in
the U.S. and Canada, benefit accruals will cease December 31, 2019.
